# Golang — Test Patterns

## Stack context
- Go 1.18+, standard `testing` package
- testify (`github.com/stretchr/testify`) cho assert + mock
- mockery hoặc gomock để generate mock
- Test runner: `go test ./...`

## Phân loại test

| Cần test gì | Pattern |
|---|---|
| Pure function / usecase | Table-driven test, plain `testing.T` |
| Repository (DB) | Interface mock hoặc integration với test DB |
| HTTP handler | `httptest.NewRecorder()` + `httptest.NewServer()` |
| Kafka consumer | Interface mock cho consumer |

## Table-driven test (chuẩn Go)
```go
func TestCalculateDiscount(t *testing.T) {
    tests := []struct {
        name     string
        price    float64
        coupon   string
        expected float64
    }{
        {"valid coupon", 100.0, "SAVE10", 90.0},
        {"no coupon",    100.0, "",       100.0},
        {"invalid",      100.0, "FAKE",   100.0},
    }
    for _, tt := range tests {
        t.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {
            got := CalculateDiscount(tt.price, tt.coupon)
            assert.Equal(t, tt.expected, got)
        })
    }
}
```

## Mock với testify/mock
```go
type MockUserRepo struct { mock.Mock }

func (m *MockUserRepo) FindByID(id string) (*User, error) {
    args := m.Called(id)
    return args.Get(0).(*User), args.Error(1)
}

func TestGetUser(t *testing.T) {
    repo := new(MockUserRepo)
    repo.On("FindByID", "123").Return(&User{ID: "123"}, nil)
    svc := NewUserService(repo)
    user, err := svc.GetUser("123")
    assert.NoError(t, err)
    assert.Equal(t, "123", user.ID)
    repo.AssertExpectations(t)
}
```

## HTTP handler test
```go
func TestLoginHandler(t *testing.T) {
    body := `{"username":"admin","password":"secret"}`
    req := httptest.NewRequest(http.MethodPost, "/login", strings.NewReader(body))
    req.Header.Set("Content-Type", "application/json")
    w := httptest.NewRecorder()

    handler := NewLoginHandler(mockAuthService)
    handler.ServeHTTP(w, req)

    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusOK, w.Code)
}
```

## Test naming convention
```
Test{FunctionName}_{Condition}_{ExpectedBehavior}
TestGetUser_NotFound_ReturnsError
```

## Quy tắc
- Mock interface, không mock struct cụ thể.
- Mỗi test file tên `*_test.go`, cùng package với code hoặc package `..._test`.
- `t.Parallel()` cho test độc lập để chạy nhanh hơn.
- Integration test: dùng build tag `//go:build integration` để chạy tách biệt.
- Chạy chỉ unit: `go test ./... -short`
- Chạy integration: `go test ./... -tags=integration`
